name: The Two Door Hanbury Sideboard
description: Timeless and tasteful the Hanbury cabinet is sure to create an indulgent interior. Finished in any of DAVIDSONs lustrous finishes, the highlight of this cabinet is the eye-drawing radial pattern to the doors and the opulent polished nickel handles that have a shagreen inlay. The cabinet looks particularly wonderful finished in two different timbers that compliment each other beautifully on the eye. The doors open on push latches to reveal a satin interior to match the exterior casing. The Hanbury would make a statement on its own or as a duo in sitting room, dining room or bedroom alcoves offering refined storage in a wide range of beautiful, tinted wood and lacquer options and sizes.
